{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/502","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/502/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/502/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/502/events","html_url":"https://github.com/willmcgugan/rich/issues/502","id":768243178,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU3NjgyNDMxNzg=","number":502,"title":"[BUG] word joiner characters can break table row layout","user":{"login":"robinwhittleton","id":7414,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc0MTQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/7414?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton","html_url":"https://github.com/robinwhittleton","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":2200581776,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwyMjAwNTgxNzc2","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/labels/Needs%20triage","name":"Needs triage","color":"bfdadc","default":false,"description":""}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":3,"created_at":"2020-12-15T22:03:48Z","updated_at":"2020-12-17T07:55:19Z","closed_at":"2020-12-16T09:30:18Z","author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"**Describe the bug**\r\nWhen the text in a table has [word joiner characters](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Word_joiner) in it, the width of the row can be miscalculated, causing borders to overflow to the next line.\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\n```\r\nfrom rich.console import Console\r\nfrom rich.table import Table\r\n\r\nconsole = Console()\r\n\r\ntable_with_wjs = Table()\r\ntable_with_wjs.add_column(\"Problem with word joiner characters\")\r\ntable_with_wjs.add_row(\"word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2 word1⁠word2\")\r\nconsole.print(table_with_wjs)\r\n\r\ntable_without_wjs = Table()\r\ntable_without_wjs.add_column(\"No problem without word joiner characters\")\r\ntable_without_wjs.add_row(\"word1word2 word1word2 word1word2 word1word2 word1word2 word1word2 word1word2 word1word2 word1word2 word1word2 word1word2 word1word2 word1word2\")\r\nconsole.print(table_without_wjs)\r\n\r\n```\r\n(note that there are word joiner characters in between each `word1` and `word2` strings in the first table)\r\n\r\nThis renders like this:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"588\" alt=\"Screenshot 2020-12-15 at 23 01 14\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7414/102278132-91f69f00-3f29-11eb-8001-42d550d904a4.png\">\r\n\r\n**Platform**\r\nmacOS 11.0.1, Apple Terminal (also tested in iTerm2), rich 9.4.0, font is Fira Mono but I’ve tested with most other pre-installed mono fonts and Source Code Pro.","closed_by":{"login":"robinwhittleton","id":7414,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc0MTQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/7414?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton","html_url":"https://github.com/robinwhittleton","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robinwhittleton/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"performed_via_github_app":null}